    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a driver-focused E92 M3 powered by the high-revving S65 4.0L V8, delivering linear power delivery up to an 8,400 RPM redline. This specimen features the preferred 6-speed manual gearbox and a variable M differential lock, ensuring precise torque distribution. The suspension geometry remains true, equipped with Electronic Damper Control (EDC) for versatile damping characteristics. Critical preventative maintenance, including rod bearings and throttle actuators, has been addressed to preserve the integrity of the powertrain. While the finish exhibits minor stone chips typical of an active enthusiast vehicle, the structural and mechanical components are robust, offering a pure analog driving experience.",
      "price": 34500.0,
