    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a prime example of a well-maintained daily driver that balances performance with practicality. The exterior finish remains vibrant, showing only minor, age-typical stone chips and light surface marks that are barely noticeable from a distance. Inside, the cabin has been kept in impressive condition; the upholstery is free of tears, the dashboard is crack-free, and all electronic features\u2014including the infotainment system and climate control\u2014function exactly as they should. Under the hood, the engine remains responsive and quiet, benefited by a strict adherence to the manufacturer\u2019s service schedule. Recent maintenance includes a fresh oil change, new air filters, and a comprehensive brake system check. The tires have ample tread remaining, and the transmission shifts smoothly through every gear. This car offers a reliable, comfortable driving experience for anyone looking for a vehicle that has been treated with care and attention to detail.",
      "price": 36500.0,
